Package: MethylRegion
Type: Package
Title: A Unified Framework for Differential Methylation Regions
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Xiaoqing Pan, Juanjie Wu, Yifan Yang [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Yifan Yang <yfyang.86@hotmail.com>
Authors@R: c(
    person("Xiaoqing", "Pan", role = "aut"),
    person("Juanjie", "Wu", role = "aut"),
    person("Yifan", "Yang", email = "yfyang.86@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Provides region-level methylation analysis across case-control,
    paired treatment, continuous phenotype, and longitudinal continuous
    phenotype designs. The package unifies branch-specific AMRfinder prototypes
    into a single MethylRegion API with separate functions for DMR and AMR
    study designs.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
    stats
Suggests:
    lmerTest
URL: https://github.com/godot4k/MethylRegion
BugReports: https://github.com/godot4k/MethylRegion/issues
